author: NashDishesDimes
title: Just how good is Cards run game?
text: Just how good is Cards run game? Glad you asked... Chris Johnson 2nd in the NFL in rushing WOW Join Date: Aug 2012 Posts: 2,541 That's better than I realized. The only team ahead of us is Seattle and 3rd place is SF. I get the feeling that StL will be quickly shooting to the top of the rushing charts as well so that will be all 4 teams in the NFC West leading the rushing charts. Granted both Seattle and SF have QBs that like to run and we don't so we are relying solely on our RBs for our rush yards.
